Class WumpusCave

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class WumpusCave
extends java.lang.Object
    Artificial Intelligence A Modern Approach (3rd Edition): page 236.

    The wumpus world is a cave consisting of rooms connected by passageways. The rooms are always organized into a grid. See Figure 7.2 for an example.
    Author:
    Federico Baron, Alessandro Daniele, Ciaran O'Reilly
